### Describe the feature you would like

anvil API has send_impersonate_transaction which is a helper that bypasses any tx signing and sends the tx as is.

ideally we have a way to also impersonate and undo imperosnate at the same time.

for this we can create a new future type that takes the tx request, if the tx request has a from field,
we impersonate first, then send the request, then undo impersonate

